SASE (Secure Access Service Edge):

Cloud-based

Combines networking + security

Ideal for remote/hybrid workers

Secures access to cloud apps and data centers

ğŸ§ª Testing & Environment Knowledge

Partially Known Environment (Gray Box Test):

Tester has limited knowledge (IP ranges, OS, etc.)

Focuses testing effort efficiently

Jump Server:

Acts as a controlled gateway

Prevents direct access to internal resources

